, 则有
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\binom{n}{k}+\binom{n}{k+m}+\binom{n}{k+2m}+\cdots=\frac{1}{m}\sum_{t=0}^{m-1}\left(2\cos\frac{t\pi}{m}\right)^{n}\cos\frac{(n-2k)t\pi}{m}.
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

