\begin_layout Proposition
记
\begin_inset Formula $\omega=\exp\left(\frac{2\pi\ui}{m}\right)$
\end_inset

是1的
\begin_inset Formula $m$
\end_inset

次根, 则对于任一多项式
\begin_inset Formula $P(x)=\sum_{r}a_{r}x^{r}$
\end_inset

有
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\frac{1}{m}\sum_{t=0}^{m-1}\omega^{-kt}P\left(\omega^{t}x\right)=a_{k}x^{k}+a_{k+m}x^{k+m}+a_{k+2m}x^{k+2m}+\cdots.
\]

\end_inset


